    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior has no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior is clean and unworn, with all upholstery, surfaces, and components in like-new condition. Mechanically, the car runs perfectly with no known issues. All features and systems function as intended.",
